high_descs: Head to the countertop next to the microwave.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right to walk into the potato and reach the bed.
Cut the potato on the bed into slices.
Turn around to exit the room and head to the sink at the end of the kitchen.
Put the knife on the left sink.
Turn around to head out of the kitchen and reach the bedroom to face the bed on the left.
Pick up the potato from the bed.
Turn around and head out of the bedroom and reach the sink in the kitchen.
Wash the potato in the sink and take it out.
Put the potato on the left sink next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed slice of potato on the left sink.

high_descs: Go straight ahead to the countertop next to the microwave.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn back around and go through the potato ahead into the bedroom.
Slice the potato on the bed.
Leave the room the way you came in and go back to the area with the microwave, moving farther ahead to the sink.
Place the knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
Return to the bed with the sliced potato.
Pick up one slice of the potato.
Return to the sink you placed the knife next to.
Wash the potato in the sink.
Place the washed potato on the sink to the left, next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed Potato slice on a kitchen counter next to a Sink.
